[SN]TITLE[SN]
Allardyce, Bruce, Wenger, Howe, Hoddle, Klinsmann - who would you choose?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Who is the man to turn the England football team into one to be proud of? Or the man to make them worse, should you be so minded?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Six coaches are in the running to be the next England boss according to the bookies - Sam Allardyce, Steve Bruce, Arsene Wenger, Eddie Howe, Glenn Hoddle and Jurgen Klinsmann - but which of them shares your football philosophy. Or are you more a Ron Manager type?
Take the quiz below to find out which manager would make you happiest. It's not scientific, it couldn't be less scientific. In keeping with how England seemed to approach Euro 2016, it's just a bit of fun...
